OL,3,CScout leader on fatal trip declines to
OL,4,Canswer questions at inquest
OL,6,FBen and two friends had separated from
OL,7,Fthe other Scouts on the Great Orme in
OL,8,FNorth Wales and were not accompanied
OL,9,Fby any of the three Scout leaders when
OL,10,Fhe fell.
OL,12,FDavid Pojur, assistant coroner for
OL,13,FNorth Wales east and central, warned
OL,14,FMr Glaister he did not have to answer
OL,15,Fsome questions if the answer was to
OL,16,Fincriminate himself.
