OL,6,FThe inquest jury has heard suggestions
OL,7,FMr Glaister had believed another man,
OL,8,FBrian Garraway, group Scout leader,
OL,9,Fwas also going on the trip, only to
OL,10,Fdiscover he was not present when he
OL,11,Fgot to their campsite in Snowdonia.
OL,13,FIt meant no suitably qualified first
OL,14,Faider was present for the trip, .
OL,16,FBernard Richmond KC, representing
OL,17,FBen's family for law firm Fieldfisher,
OL,18,Fquestioned Mr Glaister about this, but
OL,19,Fhe declined to answer a series of
OL,20,Fquestions.
