OL,3,CScout leader on fatal trip declines to
OL,4,Canswer questions at inquest
OL,6,FMr Richmond said: "You knew he was not
OL,7,Fcoming on that weekend before you
OL,8,Fstarted, didn't you?
OL,10,F"You have maintained a lie about this
OL,11,Fto this family for five years, haven't
OL,12,Fyou?
OL,14,F"You have pretended, at Christmas and
OL,15,Fbirthdays, to this family how
OL,16,Fdevastated you are about Ben's loss,
OL,17,Fwhilst all the time lying in front of
OL,18,Fthem to an inquest jury, haven't you?"
OL,20,FEach time Mr Glaister responded, "I
OL,21,Fprefer not to answer."
