OL,6,F"But you never told them to, did you?"
OL,7,FMr Richmond said.
OL,9,F"No," Mr Glaister replied.
OL,11,FThe witness agreed The Scout
OL,12,FAssociation never monitored his
OL,13,Factivities or ensured any training he
OL,14,Fwas supposed to undergo had ever been
OL,15,Fdone.
OL,17,FMr Richmond added: "They have hung you
OL,18,Fout to dry, haven't they?"
